  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Un es tspohſtischu Pa-\ntroſu/ un darrischu weenu Ug-\nguni eekſch Joana/ un es turre-\nschu Sohdibas eekſch No.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Un es iſqahſischu fatwu\nBahrfibu pahr Sinn to Egiptes\nStiprumu/ un tsdeldefschu to\nPuſka eekſch No.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Un es eededſinaschti Ug-\nguni Egiptes-Semmê/ Sin zee-\ntihs leelas Sahpes/ un No tapę\nfatckelts/ un Nowę buhs ikdee-\nnas baiſges.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "17. Tee Jaunekti no Awena\nan Pibosetes krittihs zaar Soh-\nbinn/ un tahs (Seewas) ees\nZeetuma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "18. Un eekſch Takwanefa taps\nta Gaisma aptumichota/ kad es\nto Egiptes Juhgu tur fatreek-\nſchu/ un to Lepnibu winnas\nStipruma eekſch winnas nobeiſ-\nſchu/ weena Padebbes aptlabs\nriann/ un winnas Meitas ees\nZeetuma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "19. Ta turreſchu es Sohdi-\nas Egiptes-Semmê/ un tee fa-\nuttihs/ ka es ejmu tas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "20. Ir weenupadeſmita Gad-\na pirma Mehneti/ ſeptita Dee-\nna tahs Mehnes/ notikke ta\nKUNGA Wahros us man/ kas\nazzija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "21. Tu Zilweka Behrus/ Es\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "efnu Warauis ta Egiptes Reh-\nnina Elkonus fatreezis/ un raugi/\ntas ne tapę fafeets zaar Plah-\nſtern Uslifſchann/ zaar Antu\nPeelikſchann/ zaar winna Sa-\nfaitſſchannu/ ka tas warretu to\nSohbinn turreht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Tapehz ta faſka tas Kunge\nKUNGS: Redsi/ Es gribbu\nprett Warauii to Egiptes Rehut-\nnu/ un es fatreeſſchu winna El-\nkonus/ tik labbi to Stipro ka to\nSatreeſto/ un es liſſchu win-\nnam to Sohbinu no winna Roh-\nlas iſkrift.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Un es iſkaiſischu tohs E-\ngipterus starp teem Paganeem/\nun iſputtinaschti tohs Walstis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "24. Un es stiprinaschti tohs\nElkonus ta Rehnina no Babeles/\nun dohſchu mannii Sohbinu\nwinna Rohla/ bet Warauis El-\nkonus es fatreeſſchu/ ka tan\nbuhs winna Preekſcha waideht/\nitt ka weens Eetwainohts waid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "25. Teecham/ es stiprinaschti\ntohs Elkonus ta Rehnina no Ba-\nbeles/ bet Warauis Elkoni fa-\nkrittihs/ un tee fajuttihs/ ka es\ntas KUNGS ejmu/ kad es fa-\nwn Sohbinu tam Rehnixam no\nBabeles Rohla dohſchu/ un\nwiſsch to paſchu pahr Egiptes-\nSemmi iſwilks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "26. Un es iſkaifischu tohs\nEgipterus starp teem Paga-\nneem/ un iſputtinaschti tohs\nWalstis/ ta tee fajuttihs/ ka es\ntas KUNGS ejmu.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
